-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/sanofi-aventis-secures-u-s-regulatory-authorization-for-genzyme-purchase.html
Sanofi-Aventis SA said that it has
obtained authorization from U.S. competition regulators for its
proposed acquisition of Genzyme Corp.  Sanofi published its statement on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
